Macro Definition Documentation

#define CSL_SEC_PROXY_GLOBAL_ERR_EVT_DISABLE   ((uint32_t) 0xFFFFU)

Disable global error event from being sent

#define CSL_SEC_PROXY_THREAD_STATUS_UNAVAILABLE   ((uint32_t) 0xFFFFFFFFU)

Depending on the version of the secure proxy module being used, some elements of the CSL_SecProxyThreadStatus structure are not available. In these cases, the element will have a returned value of CSL_SEC_PROXY_THREAD_STATUS_UNAVAILABLE.
